room_title: Escape room "Blackbeard's Brig" by Countdown 2 Escape in Dallas-Fort Worth
review: We did this as a mother's day present to our mother. We had a total of 4 people. We had such a blast doing it. The theme of our room was very creative. The staff was very friendly and helpful. The location was easy to locate. And very reasonable pricing. I highly recommend going here. We certainly plan on going back to try out the other rooms!
